The <strong><code>Worklet</code></strong> interface is a lightweight version of <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/Worker" title="The Worker interface of the Web Workers API represents a background task that can be easily created and can send messages back to its creator. Creating a worker is as simple as calling the Worker() constructor and specifying a script to be run in the worker thread."><code>Web Workers</code></a> and gives developers access to low-level parts of the rendering pipeline.